channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: LGBTQ Dems of Maryland Leader Caught in Child Predator Sting After Pursuing 14-Year-Old Boy
DeSantis signs bill allowing residents to kill bears, vetoes bill that fines slow left lane drivers
item.description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis signed a bill allowing people to kill black bears on their property and vetoed a bill seeking a crackdown on slow drivers in the left lane.

item.title: Abortion Access Has Won When It's Been on the Ballot. That's Not an Option for Half the States
item.description: Tucked inside the West Virginia Statehouse is a copy of a petition to lawmakers with a simple request: Let the voters decide whether to reinstate legal access to abortion.The request has been ignored by the Republican lawmakers who have supermajority control in the...

item.title: Kristi Noem at Faith & Freedom Summit: 'We Need to Focus on Winning the Hearts and Minds of People Again'
GOP governor's 'massive' appeal to Democrats could be trouble for Biden if picked as Trump's VP: insiders
item.description: Political insiders say Virginia Gov. Glenn Youngkin's bipartisan appeal could be trouble for President Biden if he's selected as former President Trump's running mate.

item.title: Trump Accuses RFK Jr. of Being 'Total Fake'
item.description: Former President Donald Trump, speaking in Philadelphia Saturday just days after the news broke that independent candidate Robert F. Kennedy Jr. and Green Party candidate Jill Stein would not qualify for next week's CNN debate, tore into Kennedy, calling him a "total fake."

item.title: Old Commie Bernie Laments on MSNBC That Billionaires Donating to Trump Signals 'Greed Over Democracy'
Balance of power: Schumer stretches reproductive rights votes further into 2024, seizing on GOP vulnerability
item.description: Schumer is planning a vote on a bill to enshrine abortion rights into law, which follows votes on contraception and IVF, in an effort to put his Republican colleagues on record.

item.title: Trump: Biden's Illegal Immigrants Targeting Americans
item.description: Former President Donald Trump, lambasting President Joe Biden Saturday night on his border policies, accused him of "releasing illegal criminals into our communities to rape, pillage, plunder and to kill" Americans.

item.title: CNN Springs Embarrassing 'Gotcha' Question on Trump and Ten Commandments, Ben Carson Was Ready
Rep. Bowman says AIPAC will see 'power of the motherf---ing Bronx' during rally speech
item.description: Rep. Jamaal Bowman of New York delivered an expletive-filled speech during a Saturday rally and blasted the US's involvement in Israel

item.title: Trump: Biden Pushing 'Fake' FBI Crime Statistics
item.description: Former President Donald Trump on Saturday accused President Joe Biden of lying about crime rates declining in the United States and of pushing "fake" FBI crime statistics and promised strong measures to fight back once he's reelected to the White House.

item.title: WATCH: Arizona Good Samaritan Dives In to Rescue Driver Whose Car Was Sinking Into Lake
Trump says 'few communities have suffered more under the Biden regime than Philadelphia' in rally stop
item.description: Trump spoke at Philadelphia's Temple University in the key swing state of Pennsylvania on Saturday, just days ahead of his first debate with President Biden.

item.title: Trump: Biden 'Dragging Us Toward WWIII'; I'll Build U.S. 'Iron Dome'
item.description: "Horrible, horrible" President Joe Biden is "dragging us toward World War III," former President Donald Trump, speaking in Philadelphia Saturday evening, declared to his supporters.
